      <h2 class="section-title">Common questions</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <button class="faq-question">Is the website really free?</button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. When you sign up for any monthly content plan, we design and build your website at no cost. There are no hidden fees, no setup charges, and no contracts. The website is yours to use as long as you're on a plan.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <button class="faq-question">Who writes the content?</button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Our team of experienced writers creates all content. They research your industry, understand your customers, and write strategic pieces designed to rank in search engines and bring real traffic to your site.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <button class="faq-question">How long before I see results?</button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>SEO is a long game, but most clients start seeing increased traffic within 2–3 months. By month 6, the compounding effect of consistent content typically delivers significant organic growth.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <button class="faq-question">Can I cancel anytime?</button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Absolutely. We ask for 30 days notice so we can wrap up any content in progress, but there are no long-term contracts or cancellation fees. If you cancel, your site stays live through the end of your billing period.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <button class="faq-question">Do I own my domain and content?</button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>You own your domain name and all the content we create for you. If you ever leave, you keep everything. We believe in earning your business every month, not locking you in.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <button class="faq-question">What if I already have a website?</button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>No problem. We can redesign your existing site for free as part of your plan, or we can work with your current site and focus purely on content creation and SEO growth. Whatever makes sense for your business.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

